headline: Pinnacle West and APS Announce Leadership Succession
summary: PHOENIX, December 12, 2024--Pinnacle West Capital Corp. Chairman and CEO Jeff Guldner will retire on March 31, 2025. APS President Ted Geisler has been tapped as his successor.
